{"tid":2346413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Trump 成為美國人“最受仰慕的男人”","createTime":"2020-12-30T08:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T13:49:51.000Z","uid":189046,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7d7ba34934384a1ae68dcfe9f85c8ca894cb91cf","tid":2346413,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:44:14.000Z","msg":"在週二（12月29日)發表的本年度蓋洛普調查結果中顯示，川普擊敗了他的前任奧巴馬，成爲美國人&ldquo;最受仰慕的男人&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n在調查問卷結果中，有18%的受訪者稱川普是自己最仰慕的男人，選擇奧巴馬的有15%，選擇拜登的有6%。川普的榜首成績結束了奧巴馬12年的&ldquo;最受仰慕的男人&rdquo;生涯。<br />\n<br />\n另外有3%的人選擇美國國家過敏和傳染病研究所所長安東尼&middot;福西（Anthony Fauci），2％的人選擇教宗弗朗西斯（Francis）。<br />\n<br />\n其餘前十名男子包括商人埃隆&middot;馬斯克（Elon Musk）、佛蒙特州參議員伯尼&middot;桑德斯（Bernie Sanders）、微軟聯合創始人兼慈善家比爾&middot;蓋茨（Bill Gates）、籃球運動員勒布朗&middot;詹姆斯（LeBron James）和藏傳佛教徒的精神領袖達賴喇嘛。<br />\n<br />\nBreitbart新聞評論認爲，川普一年中在整個公衆意識中的崛起一直是緩慢卻穩定的。今年是川普第十次躋身於前十人之列，這包括了他進入政黨政治之前的四次 （1988年至1990年和2011年）。<br />\n<br />\n蓋茨總共有21次躋身前十，奧巴馬15次，達賴喇嘛11次。拜登曾在2018年入圍十一次，而福西和詹姆斯此次是新入圍。<br />\n<br />\n於2018年去世的牧師比利&middot;格雷厄姆（Billy Graham）一生中有61次躋身前十。前總統吉米&middot;卡特（Jimmy Carter）是活着的躋身前十次數最多的人，共有29次，于格雷厄姆（Graham）和羅納德&middot;里根（Ronald Reagan）後，在歷史上排名第三。卡特（Carter）今年名列前十名之外，但進入了2019年的榜單。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/458458?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F458458%3Flang%3Db5&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=14989829\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/458458?lang=b5</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc5924fea618462d4efac8240afc6502b9028a11","tid":2346413,"uid":158613,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T08:54:45.000Z","msg":"美國人一定好鍾意賭錢<br />\n有成21%人&quot;仰慕&quot; 老千貪腐集團<br />\n(奧巴馬15%，拜登6%)"},{"pid":"ad0c499759e4b26f6bb3b27f60ff2434b751c506","tid":2346413,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1ee2f71e04a1a5bfdd96752d5e8483116db45b","tid":2346413,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"pence型好多囉"},{"pid":"51ed24aa6e52c88441983b3f318331c2b63be6e5","tid":2346413,"uid":83328,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:38:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/dc/95/1b/dc951ba97d8218e04ad1b22c34d710b6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fdc%2F95%2F1b%2Fdc951ba97d8218e04ad1b22c34d710b6.jpg&h=73df288d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/facebook/001/107/494/121.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Ffacebook%2F001%2F107%2F494%2F121.png&h=f7ee8281&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e9f3dd6d8a977e26d055bdde1a75ebe7682492e","tid":2346413,"uid":238415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"呢度都係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237919380dbbe1989e726d4503c2f4e9cab07681","tid":2346413,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e9f3dd6d8a977e26d055bdde1a75ebe7682492e","tid":2346413,"uid":238415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"呢度都係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Trump"},{"pid":"5388b3a0abc2b42ff3ff490bcb898cb9b55fb40b","tid":2346413,"uid":37723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"拜登成為美國兒童&quot;最受仰慕男人&quot;"},{"pid":"22864a010f18e82db38be905f4b79ac3a88bb779","tid":2346413,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"